{"word":"εὐστομέω","slug":"εὐστομέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εὐστομέω</b></el> <el>(εὐστομέω,) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to sing sweetly</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>generally, = <a href='S:εὐφημέω'><el>εὐφημέω</el></a>, <i>to refrain from speech</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:εὔστομος'><el>εὔστομος</el></a>\n"}]}